comment: /**  * Execute a command using the specified arguments, and using the specified expression state.  * @param context the evaluation context in which the command is being executed  * @param target the target object of the call - null for static methods  * @param arguments the arguments to the executor, should match (in terms of number  * and type) whatever the command will need to run  * @return the value returned from execution  * @throws AccessException if there is a problem executing the command or the  * MethodExecutor is no longer valid  */
code: /**  * Execute a command using the specified arguments, and using the specified expression state.  * @param context the evaluation context in which the command is being executed  * @param target the target object of the call - null for static methods  * @param arguments the arguments to the executor, should match (in terms of number  * and type) whatever the command will need to run  * @return the value returned from execution  * @throws AccessException if there is a problem executing the command or the  * MethodExecutor is no longer valid  */ TypedValue execute(EvaluationContext context, Object target, Object... arguments) throws AccessException.
